  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We will identify the influence of long-term treatment of Pitavastatin compared to
      non-treatment control group on the metabolic syndrome by evaluation of a change of metabolic
      syndrome component score. And we will additionally observe the changes of CVD risk factors
      like lipid profile, abdominal fat, insulin resistance and so on.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
